      <img src='https://ghicons.github.com/assets/images/light/Education.png' alt='GitHub Education icon' height='56' width='56' class='mr-3'/>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h5">Apply for the GitHub Student Developer Pack</h2>
        <p class="text-gray text-normal mt-2">Some content goes here and continues on and on and on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
